quran[9{c,v,t}:
10,89,"Allah taala ne jawab mein farmaya “تم dono ki dua qubool ki gayi saabit qadam raho aur unn logon ke tareeqay ki hargiz pairwi nah karo jo ilm nahi rakhtay """
10,90,"aur hum bani Israel ko samandar se guzaar le gay phir firaon aur is ke lashkar zulm aur zayad-ti ki gharz se un ke peechay chalay hatta ke jab firaon doobnay laga to bol utha"" mein ne maan liya ke khudawand haqeeqi uss ke siwa koi nahi hai jis par bani Israel imaan laaye, aur mein bhi sir itaat jhuka dainay walon mein se hon """
10,91,( jawab diya gaya ) “اab imaan lata hai! halaank iss se pehlay taq to nafarmani karta raha aur fasaad barpaa karne walon mein se tha
10,92,"ab to hum sirf teri laash hi ko bachayen ge taakay to baad ki naslon ke liye nishaan Ibrat banay agarchay bohat se ensaan aisay hain jo hamari nshanyon se ghaflat brtte hain """
10,93,hum ne bani Israel ko bohat acha thikana diya aur nihayat umdah wasail zindagi inhen ataa kiye phir unhon ne baahum ikhtilaaf nahi kya mgras waqt jabkay ilm unn ke paas aa chuka tha yaqeenan tera rab qayamat ke roz unn ke darmain uss cheez ka faisla kar day ga jis mein woh ikhtilaaf karte rahay hain
10,94,"ab agar tujhe uss hadaayat ki taraf se kuch bhi shak ho jo hum ne tujh par nazil ki hai to unn logon se pooch le jo pehlay se kitaab parh rahay hain fi al waqea yeh tairay paas haq hi aaya hai tairay rab ki taraf se, lehaza to shak karne walon mein se nah ho"
10,95,"aur un logon mein nah shaamil ho jinhon ne Allah ki ayaat ko jhtlaya hai, warna to nuqsaan uthany walon mein se hoga"
10,96,haqeeqat yeh hai ke jin logon par tairay rab ka qoul raast agaya hai un ke samnay khuwa koi nishani aa jaye
10,97,woh kabhi imaan laa kar nahi dete jab taq ke dard naak azaab samnay aata nah dekh len
